      "message": "Thanks for the review. Removed all properties and reverted to empty object in the new patchset, so there\u0027s nothing to fill out now.\nThe intended use case is drive inventory discovery, a separate daemon would watch for this interface on D-Bus to know which drives are present. The companion design doc (change [89404]) describes the proposed usage.\n\n[89404]:\nhttps://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/docs/+/89404",
